nodes.text: Gak's was a cantina, that was located on Kwenn Space Station.

In 3 ABY, a group of Alliance to Restore the Republic agents traveled to Gak's, to rendezvous with the Bothan agent Corl'ya. However, Corl'ya didn't make it there and after the agents had waited in the cantina for an hour, they decided to leave and return to their ship.
